See: https://gist.github.com/srkiNZ84/7380acc9260b54ba99b7 for s3 backup setup etc...

Sample "append only" policy is:

{
    "Version": "2012-10-17",
    "Statement": [
        {
            "Effect": "Allow",
            "Action": [
                "s3:Get*",
                "s3:List*",
                "s3:PutObject"
            ],
            "Resource": "*"
        }
    ]
}
